            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(C.) In nomine sancte+ et individue+ trinitatis. <persName ref="#people/7"
                            key="#Emperor/king">Otto</persName> div[ina favente clement]ia <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus. Si aecclesiis dei devote
                        que+ famulantes eis petierint contulerimus, aeternae recompensationis
                        premium procul dubio accipere non ambigimus. Quapropter omnium sancte+ dei
                        aecclesiae fidelium nostrorumque presentium scilicet ac futurorum noverit
                        sagacitatis industria, quomodo nos interventu <persName key="#Bishops"
                            >Adelberti</persName> nostri dilecti <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs>
                        per <rs key="#Imperial/royal_diploma">nostram preceptalem paginam</rs>
                        confirmavimus <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs><orgName
                            key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/1423"> sancti Petri in Ce+lo
                            aureo</orgName> cui <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/3960"
                            >Azo</persName> venerabilis <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> preesse
                        videtur, omnem <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terram</rs> quam in partibus
                        Tuscie+ habere visum est, per diversos <rs key="#Comitatus">comitatus</rs>
                        vel loca, scilicet in <geogName ref="#estates/83" key="#Comitatus">comitatu
                            Florentino</geogName><rs key="#Curtes"> curtem </rs><geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Churches" ref="#estates/4018">Campi</geogName> cum suis
                        pertinentiis, curtem <geogName key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/4019"
                            >Granianum</geogName> cum suis pertinentiis, prope curtem Campi <rs
                            key="#Churches">e+cclesiam </rs>unam cum suis pertinentiis, in <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Churches #Aldius" ref="#estates/4020"><placeName
                                ref="#places/4906">Linare</placeName></geogName> curtem cum
                        aecclesia et suis pertinentiis, in ipso Linare <rs key="#Aldius"
                            >aldiones</rs> decem, in <geogName key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/4021"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/4907">Olena</placeName></geogName> curtem
                        unam cum pertinentiis suis, infra <rs key="#Cities">civitatem</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/2"><geogName
                                key="#Houses #Curtes #Fruits/vegetables #Churches"
                                ref="#estates/159">Florentiam</geogName></placeName> curtem unam cum
                        aecclesia et <rs key="#Houses">casa cum tribus caminatis et uno solario</rs>
                        et duobus <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables">ortis</rs> et omnibus aliis suis
                        pertinentiis, in <geogName key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/4022"><placeName
                                ref="#places/4908">Ramiano</placeName></geogName> curtem unam cum
                        suis pertinentiis, in <geogName key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/4023"
                            >Gallinone</geogName> curticellam unam, in <placeName key="#Manentes"
                            >Blaude</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Manentes">manentem</rs> unum, in <placeName ref="#places/506"
                                ><geogName key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/4024"
                            >Fesule</geogName></placeName> curtem unam, in <placeName
                            ref="#places/4909"><geogName key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/4025"
                                >Rontet</geogName></placeName> curtem unam, in <geogName
                            key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/4026"><placeName ref="#places/4910"
                                >Cellule</placeName></geogName> curtem unam cum suis [pert]inentiis,
                        in <geogName key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/4027">Saniano</geogName> curtem
                        unam, in Casaentino curtem unam, in <geogName key="#Curtes"
                            ref="#estates/4028">Maurana</geogName> curtem unam, in
                        <geogName key="#Curtes"
                            ref="#estates/4029">Mediana</geogName> curtem unam cum pertinentiis suis, in [...
                        cur]tem unam, <geogName key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/4030">curtem <placeName ref="#places/4912">Tartilese</placeName></geogName> cum suis pertinentiis,
                        <geogName key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/4031">curtem Olenam</geogName> prope <orgName>plebem sancti
                            Uiti</orgName> sitam et quicquid in decimo Manisso[...]o, in fine
                        Florentie+, in Uallia, in Sufficuano, in Orbanula, prope montem sancti
                        Martini et iuxta<orgName> plebem sanctae Mariae in Octinula</orgName> seu in
                        Maurana vel in aliis quibuscumque locis predictum monasterium habere
                        videtur, cum familiis utriusque sexus et omnibus aliis rebus eidem
                        monasterio pertinentibus, ea videlicet ratione quatinus predictus abbas ac
                        sui successores de omnibus prescriptis rebus habeant potestatem possidendi
                        ordinandi disponendi vel quicquid eorum voluntas ad utilitatem prefati
                        monasterii decreverit faciendi, remota omnium hominum contradicione vel
                        molestatione. Si quis igitur hoc nostrum preceptum temere irrumpere
                        temptaverit, sciat se compositurum auri optimi libras centum, medietatem
                        kamerae nostrae et medietatem prelibati monasterii rectoribus. Quod ut
                        verius credatur et ab omnibus hominibus firmius dilegentiusque in posterum
                        observetur, propria manu roborantes sigillo nostro iussimus insigniri.
                        Signum domni Ottonis (MF.) invictissimi imperatoris augusti. Heribertus
                        cancellarius vice Petri episcopi et archicancellarii recognovi. (SI. D.)
                        Data XIII. kal. aug. anno dominicae incarnationis DCCCCXCVI, indictione
                        VIIII, anno vero tercii Ottonis [regnantis XIII, imper]ii autem eius
                        pr[im]o; actum Marila; feliciter amen.</ab>
